Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_stt

The shadow TX trigger register is a shadow register for the TX trigger bits (MIO_UART(0..1)_FCR[TXTRIG]) that can be used to remove the burden of having to store the previously written value to MIO_UART(0..1)_FCR in memory and having to mask this value so that only the TX trigger bits get updated.
